title: Grand Theft Auto - FPSRussia
description:
With WWIII hitting Las Venturas, a Zombie Apocalypse infested San Fierro, and having everything he knows and loves taken away in Las Santos... Dmitri Potapoff must do anything and everything to keep him and his Youtube channel alive.

Grand Theft Auto - FPSRussia is a major modification to GTA San Andreas. It is designed to bring out the best graphics without sacrificing to much performance compared to hundreds of other graphic mods being barely playable by most users. Along with that, the game comes with many familiar faces from Youtube such as FPSRussia, Whiteboy7thst, Paintball Kitty, and Woodysgamertag who all share a part in a dangerous life changing journey. This mod will suit any GTA or FPRussia fan out there, hope you enjoy!
